content.name: cdi_map_adm_producer_bronze_load

object.customQuery:
with current_batch as (
select
	bls.batch_id,
	bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
	bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
from
	$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
where
	bls.source_system_code ='$$sourcesystemcode'
	and bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	and bls.batch_id = (
	select
		MAX(batch_id)
	from
		$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
	where
		source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
		and batch_status = 'Inprogress' ) )
select
	distinct
	 source_name, 
metal_ap.load_type, 
metal_ap.id, 
metal_ap.last_name, 
metal_ap.first_name, 
metal_ap.middle_name, 
metal_ap.suffix, 
metal_ap.term_flag, 
metal_ap.misc_flags, 
metal_ap.fid_num, 
metal_ap.fid_type, 
metal_ap.active, 
metal_ap.npn_number, 
metal_ap.resident_state, 
metal_ap.created, 
metal_ap.modified,
current_batch.batch_id
from
	$$raw_schema.adm_producer metal_ap
cross join current_batch
order by
	metal_ap.id,
	metal_ap.created,
	metal_ap.modified;
